<div id="mcontent">
<p class="headinfo">Assist and inspire students to prepare for, connect to, and get involved in their BYU-Idaho learning experience.</p>
<div id="blocks">
<div class="block"><img src="images/student-support/mission/pic2.jpg" />
<div class="blockinfo">
<h3>Assist</h3>
<p>Students will ASSIST new and current students, parents and other by answering questions, resolving concerns, giving counsel, and directing them to the services and resources needed.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="block"><img src="images/student-support/mission/pic1.jpg" />
<div class="blockinfo">
<h3>Inspire</h3>
<p>Students will INSPIRE one another and those they work with they strive to "bring down the powers of heaven" and recognize the hand of the Lord throughout their service.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="block"><img src="images/student-support/mission/pic5.jpg" />
<div class="blockinfo">
<h3>Prepare</h3>
<p>Students will help new and current students to PREPARE for and participate in the BYU-Idaho disciple preparation center experience.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="block"><img src="images/student-support/mission/pic4.jpg" />
<div class="blockinfo">
<h3>Connect</h3>
<p>Students will help new and current students CONNECT to fellow students, faculty and administration and to BYU-Idaho</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="block"><img src="images/student-support/mission/pic3.jpg" />
<div class="blockinfo">
<h3>Involve</h3>
<p>Students will help new and current students GET INVOLVED to strengthen their disciple leadership for future service in the Church, family, workplace, and community.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
